casebody.data:
Ron J. RODS, Petitioner, v. DEPARTMENT OF THE INTERIOR, Respondent. No. 2006-3424. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Nov. 6, 2006.

Official Caption 3

. Required for use on petitions, formal briefs and appendices, court opinions, and dispositive court orders. FRAP 12(a); 32(a).

ORDER

The order of dismissal and the mandate dated October 31, 2006 having been issued in error,

IT IS ORDERED THAT:

(1) The order of dismissal issued October 31, 2006 is vacated, the mandate recalled, and the petition for review is reinstated.

(2) Petitioner’s brief is due on or before December 19, 2006.
